Package corewar

Package containing the CoreWar.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cell
    Object representing one Cell from the MARS.
    Checker
    Executable class used to check if .red doesn't contain illegal instructions.
    Interpreter
    Object holding the core with it's memory and the interpreter to play each cycle.
    Main
    Executable class to run a game with the given programs as parameters.
    Memory
    Object representing the memory of the game.
    Operand
    Object representing one Operand from a Cell
    Parser
    Object used to read .red program and turn it into a List of Cells that can be used by the Interpreter.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Instruction
    Enum represeting the diffrents Instructions.
    Type
    Enum represeting the diffrents Operand Type.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IllegalInstructionException
    Custom Exception to handle illegal instructions.
